.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
The people use 5 different means of transport: train, motorbike, subway, taxi, tram
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: techno, house, hip-hop, electronic, trance
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: iris, azalea, dahlia, daisy, poppy
The people have 5 different hobbies: card-games, sudoku, baking, skydiving, board-games
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: skiing, sailing, tennis, surfing, baseball

1. the fan of techno is the person driving the train
2. the fan of house is the person who's sport is skiing
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person driving the motorbike
4. the fan of hip-hop is the person who's hobby is sudoku
5. the person driving the motorbike is to the right of the person driving the subway
6. the person who growsiris is the person who's sport is baseball
7. the person who growsazalea is the person driving the taxi
8. the person who's hobby is baking is in the middle
9. the fan of electronic is on the far left
10. the person who growsdahlia is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing
11. the person who growsazalea is to the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing
12. the person who growsdaisy is the person who's hobby is skydiving
13. the fan of trance is the person who growspoppy
14. the fan of electronic is to the left or right of the person driving the tram

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| Music-Genre	|   electronic	|    hip-hop	|     techno	|    house	|    trance	|
| Transport		|    taxi	|      tram	|      train	|     subway	|     motorbike	|
| Hobby	|     board-games	|      sudoku	|      baking	| skydiving	|     card-games	|
| Flower		|     azalea	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| daisy	|   parliament	|
| Sport		|     sailing	|     surfing	|     baseball	|     skiing	|     tennis	|
